{"tid":1231191,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日想多謝Apple Store","createTime":"2019-06-16T11:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T16:13:40.000Z","uid":110459,"like":76,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"afc6f65fffcba63b0068b9cf5186698cf42059b5","tid":1231191,"uid":110459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T11:59:09.000Z","msg":"今日約咗朋友喺銅鑼灣apple store集合出發遊行，但嗰時地鐵塞死晒朋友唔知點樣上到嚟，有位員工聽到就叫我同朋友講邊個出口仲出到。<br />\n<br />\n之後諗住就嚟1430夠鐘行過去維園出發遊行，屌個商場所有出入口都塞死晒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知啲員工走咗唔不斷叫人「經我哋依邊樓梯落去啦！商場嗰邊行唔到」入返去啲員工都係咁同黑衫同伴講辛苦晒！加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe5f6fd0d9be43eb73926f6823211dfebf7d145e","tid":1231191,"uid":186152,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:05:45.000Z","msg":"廢老 : 外國勢力又干涉"},{"pid":"257f0673802da2606eff66ef42c6effa5fe8b928","tid":1231191,"uid":78666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:06:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99aec708cf83e54ada089b852fdb99fa36aa7f5a","tid":1231191,"uid":231758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe5f6fd0d9be43eb73926f6823211dfebf7d145e","tid":1231191,"uid":186152,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:05:45.000Z","msg":"廢老 : 外國勢力又干涉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65290823c2ecef7d9afa437847a62cefbbd2a2f","tid":1231191,"uid":110459,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fe5f6fd0d9be43eb73926f6823211dfebf7d145e","tid":1231191,"uid":186152,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:05:45.000Z","msg":"廢老 : 外國勢力又干涉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:10: